 and shear moduli of the NbO\nphase are comparable to the WN$_x$ compounds that have been claimed to be\nultra-compressible for superhard.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Mar 2014 21:32:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
