k antiferromagnetic modulation of the primary ferrimagnetic\norder, and a fractionalized skyrmion phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Mar 2014 13:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-06"}
